== 制作 ==
这部电影在杀青前经历了各种制作上的挑战，涉及演员、拍摄进度、拍摄地点以及预算方面的考虑。<ref name="R1">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/filmNews/idUSTRE55T0RU20090630|title=Action pic "Unstoppable" hits budget snags|last=Zeitchik|first=Steven|date=June 30, 2009|work=reuters.com|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=August 17, 2009|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126080415/https://www.reuters.com/article/filmNews/idUSTRE55T0RU20090630|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="V4">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118005944.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&query=Martin+Campbell|title=Denzel Washington exits 'Unstoppable'|last=Fleming|first=Michael|date=July 13, 2009|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=August 17, 2009}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

在2007年6月，[[20世纪福克斯|20世纪福克斯]]当时与[[马丁·坎贝尔|马丁·坎贝尔]]协商关於执导此电影一事，<ref name="V1">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118005527.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|title=Fox dealing with 'Unstoppable' budget|last=Fleming|first=Michael|date=June 7, 2007|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=August 17, 2009|archive-date=2009-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091014182024/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118005527.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>当时他被告知是导演，直到2009年3月才轉由[[東尼·史考特|東尼·史考特]]正式担任导演。<ref name="V3">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/VR1118001755.html|title=Tony Scott boards 'Unstoppable'|last=Fleming|first=Michael|date=March 27, 2009|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=August 17, 2009|archive-date=2010-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100104032624/http://www.variety.com/VR1118001755.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>4月时，丹泽尔·华盛顿和克里斯·潘恩都陸續參與电影製演。<ref name="V2">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117966502.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|title=Fox train thriller just 'Unstoppable'|last=Fleming|first=Michael|date=June 29, 2009|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=August 17, 2009|archive-date=2007-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071117190400/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117966502.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

因為經費考量，原来電影预算由1亿7百万美元削减到1亿美元，但福克斯仍想将预算继续削减到9千万美元以下的范围，除了要求导演斯科特将其薪酬从9百万美元降低到6百万美元外，也希望主角丹泽尔·华盛顿将他2千万美元的酬金中去掉4百万美元。<ref name="CS1">{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=57132|title=Denzel Washington Drops Out of Unstoppable?|date=July 14, 2009|publisher=Coming Soon|accessdate=August 17, 2009|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012042819/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=57132|dead-url=no}}</ref>华盛顿拒绝了这一提议，并谈到由於电影的开拍日期仍未知，他已经失去了兴趣，不过从4月起华盛顿仍參與電影進程<ref name="CM1">{{cite news|url=http://www.canmag.com/nw/14409-denzel-washington-unstoppable-again|title=Denzel Washington Unstoppable Again|last=Parsons|first=Ryan|date=July 23, 2009|publisher=CanMag|accessdate=August 17, 2009|archive-date=2019-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729185738/http://www.canmag.com/nw/14409-denzel-washington-unstoppable-again|dead-url=no}}</ref>，直到7月，他才正式从这一项目中撤出。<ref name="V4"/>之後，福克斯以修改薪資报价，2周後，他回到了電影製作。<ref name="CM1"/><ref name="V5">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118006366.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&query=Unstoppable%2C+Fox|title=Washington back on track with Fox|last=Fleming|first=Michael|date=July 22, 2009|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=August 17, 2009}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/la-et-bigpicture5-2009aug05,0,766692.story|title=In the salary tug of war between studios and talent, it's no contest|last=Goldstein|first=Patrick|date=August 5, 2009|publisher=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=August 17, 2009|archive-date=2009-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090808155618/http://www.latimes.com/la-et-bigpicture5-2009aug05,0,766692.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>

